&lt;h3 id="4-choosing-the-right-design-in-power-bi-star-schema-vs-snowflake"&gt;4. &lt;a class="link" href="https://dev.to/vishal_more_02990955c9358/choosing-the-right-design-in-power-bi-star-schema-vs-snowflake-3cdc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
